  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This magical shield is imbued with properties befitting a worshipper of Lathander, and its use is limited to those of neutral good alignment.\n\nLathander, also called the Morninglord, is the god of the spring, dawn, birth, and renewal, a god of beginning and hidden potential, a deity of conception, vitality, youth, renewal, and self-perfection. He is the commander of creativity. \n\nLathander's symbol is a simple disk of rosy pink hue. Lathander is a god of beginnings, and even individuals who worship other gods still offer a prayer to him at the start of a journey of endeavor. Lathander's name is invoked to seal alliances and start new ventures or companies. As a result, Lathander is very popular among the merchant classes, and has benefited accordingly.\n\nPriest of Lathander prefer plate mail and shield tinted to shades of red and yellow."
    }
  },
